Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:54.22,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Hear me, I say cross the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.06,0:02:00.36,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&H61B0FA&}Can you feel that nothing turns around
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.23,0:02:06.24,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&H4090B9&}Like a gear in sync inside a clock
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.07,0:02:12.28,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&H60E4E4&}Who can be sure of how to make it work
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.37,0:02:13.99,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&H60E4E4&}Recognize
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.04,0:02:15.50,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&H9BB2E5&}Inner sight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:18.50,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&H9BB2E5&}Gotta stay alive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.25,0:02:21.79,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I will never be deceived
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:24.67,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I'm a girl that sees through lies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.96,0:02:26.01,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Cuz I know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:27.84,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Know it all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:32.35,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Gonna fly so high
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.51,0:02:34.06,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Get across the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:37.52,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&HAFAA4B&}What awaits, and what can it show me now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.73,0:02:38.73,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&HAFAA4B&}Smack it down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:40.23,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&H8DC1CE&}Get across the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:43.48,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&H376D14&}Break away, and then let'em catch me say
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:45.36,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}“Don't let me down”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:46.82,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&HBEBA6D&}Oh yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.82,0:02:50.15,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&HBEBA6D&}When the clockwork moves and starts to shine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:50.95,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}(you got to find)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.95,0:02:52.78,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Forever let it blow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.99,0:02:54.41,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Carry out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.41,0:02:56.99,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&H82F7FD&}Show the way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:03:00.33,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\3c&H82F7FD&}Blast it off right
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:09.78,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}月がきれいで　僕らは恋に落ちて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:17.58,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ただ眩しいだけの夏の夜を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.83,0:23:25.46,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}愉快なメロディーで　軽いステップ踏んで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:33.55,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}笑いながら　口づけを何度でも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:41.52,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ねぇ月がきれいな夜は思い出して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.77,0:23:49.53,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}今はこんなに遠く離れても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.74,0:23:57.54,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}世界でいちばん君が大事だって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.79,0:24:08.21,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}僕がここにいて　歌っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:09.78,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}月色皎潔  我們墜入愛河
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:17.58,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}在被耀眼月光籠罩的夏夜裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.83,0:23:25.46,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}伴著愉悅的旋律  踩著輕快的舞步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:33.55,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}笑著  深深擁吻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:41.52,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}月色皎潔的夜晚就會回想起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.77,0:23:49.53,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}即便現在天各一方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.74,0:23:57.54,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}世界上最愛的還是你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.79,0:24:08.21,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我就在這裡  唱著對你的思念
